dc_description_s: This data represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners and sections for Wood County, Wisconsin in 2020. [Public Land Survey System (PLSS) control that have established survey grade GPS coordinates. Wisconsin Surveyor's Association survey grade standard: Coordinates collected under the direction of a Professional Land Surveyor, in a coordinate system allowed by s. 236.18(2), and obtained by means, methods and equipment capable of repeatable 2 centimeter or better precision.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data available, please visit: https://opendata.woodcogis.com/
